  "description": {
    "zh": "和之前一样，许多行动人员讨厌使用这些“垃圾”。他们如果拿不到多于20发的弹匣就完全不会使用这些武器，但很遗憾，明明这些都是好枪。总之，可能有理由让人们不喜欢这些弹匣，而你即将发现原因，或者人们是否对它们评价其实过于苛刻了呢。\n\n指定弹匣：\n - KAC Steel 10 7.62x51 10发\n - HK417 或 G28 7.62x51 10发弹匣",
    "en": "Same story as before, operators hate using these. They totally avoid using the guns if they cannot get their hands on the twenty-rounders, shame, because those are great guns. Anyway, maybe it has a reason that people avoid these magazines, and you are about to find out why, or if people judge it too quickly.\n\nSpecified Magazines :\n - AR-10 7.62x51 KAC 10-Round Steel Magazine\n - HK417 / G28 7.62x51 10-Round Magazine"
  },
